(62, 2, 1, 54, 2, 5, 5, 'advocate with the Father, Jesus Christ', 'Advocate and Mediator Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the role of Jesus as a mediator between God and humanity. 1 John refers to Jesus as an advocate, while 1 Timothy identifies Him as the mediator, highlighting His intercessory function.', 'theme', 0.699, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(62, 2, 1, 45, 8, 34, 34, 'we have an advocate with the Father', 'Advocacy and Intercession of Christ', 'This connection highlights the roles of Jesus as both an advocate and intercessor for believers. Both passages emphasize His position with the Father and His active support in the face of sin.', 'theme', 0.594, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
