(62, 2, 1, 47, 5, 21, 21, 'we have an advocate with the Father', 'Advocate and Righteousness Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the role of Jesus in addressing sin. In 1 John 2:1, Jesus is described as an advocate, while 2 Corinthians 5:21 highlights His righteousness and sacrificial role for humanity''s sin. This connection highlights the theme of Jesus as central to salvation and righteousness.', 'theme', 0.43999999999999995, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(62, 2, 1, 56, 2, 11, 13, 'Jesus Christ the righteous', 'Advocacy and Grace Connection', 'This connection highlights the role of Jesus Christ as both an advocate and a source of grace. Both passages emphasize living righteously and looking forward to Christ''s return, reinforcing the importance of faith in the believer''s life.', 'theme', 0.43999999999999995, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
